# Decisions Directory

This directory stores decision records.

## Naming Convention
- Format: `YYYY-MM-DD-slug.md`
- Example: `2026-02-21-memory-law.md`

## Metadata Required
- date: YYYY-MM-DD
- source: MEMORY.full.md / session / channel
- evidence: Original text snippet (≤25 chars)
- confidence: high/medium/low
